text:
Normal service and atmosphere for a takeaway food stall, so 4/5.

Food: 3/5
The batter needs to be improved. I got my waffle fresh so it was probably a good sample to judge. I liked that the exterior was crispy, but the insides were hard too. Because of that reason, the waffle felt kind of dry. Taste wise, was pretty standard - vanilla scented and not too sweet.

I will not be back.

Very delicious peanut butter waffle. The waffle was hot and tasted of eggs.

The egglets are also very tasty and warm.

They are crispy outside and soft inside.

True Hong Kong style.

Durian waffle! A premium item on the menu
